<font color="#FF0000">PING PONG BALLS &amp; WHALES</font><br>
<tt>Mon Nov  3 16:57:04 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
I'll trade you one set of whales for a forty dollar mule and two ping pong balls.<br><br>
Ping Pong Balls? Yep, we got dozens of them in Nam one day. No net, no table but hundreds of ping pong balls. Who's bright idea was it anyways to send ping pong balls to Nam?<br><br>
Used them for target practice, traded them to mamasan for cokes, even put them in the soup the seabbes cooked, but it didn't make the soup taste no better. <br>
Gosh! I just love how things all make sense now.
<p><code>-- It's all a Chinese Communist conspiracy   (Sparrowhawk) </code><p>


